  • Classes in org.rdkit.knime.nodes used by org.rdkit.knime.nodes 
    Class and Description
    AbstractRDKitCellFactory
    The root class for cell factories producing cells based on or under usage of RDKit objects.
    AbstractRDKitCellFactory.RowFailurePolicy
    This enumeration defines several policies for handling failures when processing rows during node execution.
    AbstractRDKitNodeModel
    This class can act as the super class for RDKit based KNIME nodes.
    AbstractRDKitNodeModel.ResultProcessor
    This interface implements the logic to process a result set and is passed into a ParallelProcessor constructor.
    AdditionalHeaderInfoHandler
    Deprecated. 
    Deprecated and replaced by an extension point mechanism based on HeaderPropertyHandler.
    RDKitNodePlugin
    This is the eclipse bundle activator for the RDKit Nodes Plugin.
